The state you are maintaining is not enough for that. You&#39;ve to maintain every list item&#39;s state then. You can take a key like this in every item of your list
```
{
  id: 1,
  title: &#39;...&#39;
  isEditable: false
}
```
Now when you click in an edit button, make only that item `isEditable: true`, and then render the `textarea` based on every items `isEditable` key rather than central `showTextAreaEdit` key.

